{"tid":1645113,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好俾憤怒沖昏頭腦！！！","createTime":"2019-10-10T18:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T00:47:53.000Z","uid":37679,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"24652c4a6ddfabcf2d635b441160a834ccebce42","tid":1645113,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:45:22.000Z","msg":"我知今晚好多粒核彈大家都好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問題係 有冇人覺得個timing 好鬼<br />\n陰謀論啲咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會係對家想我地升級 弒警<br />\n令到美國個法案過唔到<br />\n中英聯合聲明不被推翻<br />\n我奉勸各位手足 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">冷靜</span></span><br />\n<br />\n喺香港人權與民主法案未完全通過之前<br />\n都唔好作出太激烈既行為 i.e. 弒警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為一時之氣過唔到 我地就係咁先<br />\n我地要以大局為重<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勝利之日<br />\n清算之時</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ec33a9792800fed5d74c4911512c351fd6fb74e","tid":1645113,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:45:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be04f6cd13c750c21ef6dea33a3c9debe521c86c","tid":1645113,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:45:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa839e56d627e95169582d67e051dbf28770a4ac","tid":1645113,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:46:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"402441d8e09180f734029307ed9d8c475ff71046","tid":1645113,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite