e144ad5a83dc2a46b7fc","tid":1645113,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:21:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c604026d4b57dc400cfef4ffee6e8fc996df9048","tid":1645113,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:22:09.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過自己俾人spin緊帶緊風向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548367</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母出得啲垃圾，而家屍都搵埋，<br />\n性侵有埋人證，仲搵夠藉口比自己未？"}]}